snippet.textDisplay:
Classical is the only genre that encompasses a feeling of "boundless space" and speaks to the European soul. Stormzy will be forgotten in a year or two while the likes of Elgar, Wagner & Mozart will live forever.
Doesn't help that most modern music is absolute bilge aimed at the lowest common denominator.
